OL,3,C'What's my life right now?': the
OL,4,Cmisery of endless job rejections
OL,6,FA young woman from Shrewsbury has
OL,7,Fdescribed the misery of completing
OL,8,Fendless job applications, and getting
OL,9,Fendless rejections.
OL,11,FLyla Grace says she applied for more
OL,12,Fthan 60 jobs before successfully
OL,13,Fgetting work with Severn Trent.
OL,15,FShe said it made her feel worthless.
OL,17,F"I knew I had something to offer to
OL,18,Fdifferent work places but they just
OL,19,Fweren't giving me the time and I was
OL,20,Fjust thinking, 'what's the point?
OL,21,Fwhat's my life right now?'"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
