OL,3,C'What's my life right now?': the
OL,4,Cmisery of endless job rejections
OL,6,FShe says she ended up at home watching
OL,7,FTV, and even got bored of the TV.
OL,9,FLyla grew up in care and felt she
OL,10,Fexperienced prejudice.
OL,12,F"I think there's a stereotype around
OL,13,Fcare leavers that we're troubled,
OL,14,Fproblematic, more trouble than we're
OL,15,Fworth when that's far from the truth."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
