OL,3,C'What's my life right now?': the
OL,4,Cmisery of endless job rejections
OL,6,FAn interim report published today led
OL,7,Fby former Labour health secretary Alan
OL,8,FMilburn warned that a "whole system
OL,9,Ffailure" has led to nearly one in
OL,10,Fseven of the UK's 16 to 24-year-olds
OL,11,Fare not in employment, education or
OL,12,Ftraining, known as Neets.
OL,14,FThe report's author said there is a
OL,15,F"risk of a lost generation" and that
OL,16,FBritain "faces a generational fault
OL,17,Fline" ` but he warned there are no
OL,18,Feasy solutions.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@HO]wD@AOUwD@[O]xD@IOUyD@EO]
