OL,3,C'What's my life right now?': the
OL,4,Cmisery of endless job rejections
OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,7,FMcFadden said the government is
OL,8,F"already taking action by bringing
OL,9,Fforward the biggest youth employment
OL,10,Freforms in a generation to create
OL,11,F500,000 opportunities for young
OL,12,Fpeople."
OL,14,FLyla was taken on by Severn Trent
OL,15,Fthree years ago. She is saving for a
OL,16,Fmortgage, has her driving licence and
OL,17,Fis able to afford to go travelling.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
