OL,3,C'What's my life right now?': the
OL,4,Cmisery of endless job rejections
OL,6,FA new government scheme now aims to
OL,7,Fhelp 10,000 young people either in
OL,8,Fcare, with criminal convictions, or
OL,9,Fmental health conditions.
OL,11,FDarren Jones, the Chief Secretary to
OL,12,Fthe Treasury defended the scheme in
OL,13,Fthe face of today's unemployment
OL,14,Ffigures saying a pilot is important
OL,15,Fand it's part of a wide range of
OL,16,Fmeasures, but acknowledged there is
OL,17,Fmore to do.
